                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>think the solution of a messenger like him has been\n                                        <add>?</add>,<lb/> as he is quite unacquainted with the\n                                        English language, manners,<lb/> or customs. Some effort is\n                                        about being made in by behalf.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">My father returns you his thanks for<lb/> your\n                                        remembrance and desires me to present his kind regards to\n                                        you.<lb/> With the renewed assurance of my good wishes,</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(6)\">Believe me</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(8)\">My dear Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(9)\">Yours very truly</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Henry S. Jacobs</persName>\n                              </p>"
